Thanks for playing the tutorial level! Visit the HELP & CONTROLS screen from the Main Menu for additional information on this game's mechanics and controls. Continue unraveling the mysteries of The Spatial Junctions in the first of three exciting episodes: Into The Labs!

Find it by pressing <1> in the level selection screen.

Welcome to CPSF Industries Research Facility! You are a government agent sent to investigate a mysterious incident which took place here. Scientists were performing yet-to-be declassified experiments which altered reality itself. Nothing in this laboratory is what it seems. Reality itself has been with tampered with. Navigate through the research facility and find the  main computer. All you need to do is find the hard drive containing the experiment's data, then return it to your superiors

You may perceive a room to lie straight ahead, but space here is distorted and misleading. You may walk these halls and find that your destination isn't where you expect it to be. We've determined that these points in space where reality shifts is called a Spatial Junction. As you cross through one, your surroundings will change.

Use the W, A, S and D Keys to walk around. Use the Left and Right Arrow Keys to turn left and right. 

Some doors will be locked. You'll need to find key cards to get access to different levels of security. Blue is the lowest, Yellow is medium, and Red is high security. The main computer will be in a high security area. 

The keys that you've collected will be shown on the bottom left of your HUD. To the right of that, you can see your Energy (green) and Health (red)  levels. They're also displayed as a percentage on your HUD's Screen.

I'll show you messages from time to time to help you along your way and tell you what's going on. Call me The Operator.

I don't have access to a map of the Labs, and your perception of it's rooms and halls is subjective. You see something different than what I see because of your location in space and time. I'll try to get you to the computer room, but you'll have to get through various layers of security. 

There's a few Public Telephones scattered around the laboratory. Find them and pick up the phone. I'll get your location from there and send you on your way to the next section.

You may encounter hostile creatures that have come to our dimension through the Spatial Junctions. Use LEFT-SHIFT to fire your weapon. From our data, these enemies attack using large stingers, so don't let them touch you!

That's all I have to give you right now. Do your best, The Agency is counting on you. 

Pick up the phone, Agent.

***END TRANSMISSION***
